            "text": "Performance Optimization Strategies"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Reduce latency by leveraging HTTP/2 and connection reuse. Batch multiple synthesis requests where feasible, and cache static responses such as voice metadata. Monitor response times and adjust timeout settings based on network conditions."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "h2",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Error Handling and Monitoring Practices"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Implement retries with exponential backoff for transient errors (e.g., 5xx responses). Log detailed error messages with timestamps and request IDs for traceability. Integrate with monitoring tools to track error rates and set up alerts for anomalies."
          }
